# iso-pipeline — dynamic documentation section

## verbatim

The isometric pipeline visualization system maps every PRD-6 / PRD-7 domain type
to a 3-D coordinate in a 6-layer ZLayer stack (Document z=0 through Attestation z=5).
The X axis encodes pipeline progress; Y encodes confidence lift; Z encodes verification depth.
Each type implements `HasVisualization` returning a `VisualizationSpec` with:
- `SemanticType` — one of 12 classification categories
- `ZLayer` — z-axis stack position (0–5)
- `rhai_dsl` — a concrete Rhai snippet demonstrating the type's role in the pipeline
- `description` — a single-line human summary

The lint suite enforces this contract: all 20 tests must pass before the visualization
layer is considered sound.

Live status:
{{ cmd: cargo test -p ledger-core --test iso_lint 2>&1 | grep -E "^test result|FAILED" }}

## executive

20 domain types across 5 ZLayers implement `HasVisualization`.
Lint tests enforce description, DSL, layer index, and semantic type completeness.
SVG SMIL animation is Phase 0; rerun.io (Phase 1) and manim (Phase 2) are planned.
The z=5 Attestation layer is reserved for PRD-6-FUTURE (`ledger-attest` proc-macro).

## epigram

*The pipeline is a path through verified space — each type a point that knows where it stands.*

---

## ZLayer stack (machine-readable)

```toml
[[layer]]
index = 0
name = "Document"
color = "#334155"
base_z = 0.0
types = []

[[layer]]
index = 1
name = "Pipeline"
color = "#1d4ed8"
base_z = 136.0
types = [
  "PipelineState<Ingested>",
  "PipelineState<Validated>",
  "PipelineState<Classified>",
  "PipelineState<Reconciled>",
  "PipelineState<Committed>",
  "PipelineState<NeedsReview>",
  "CommitGate",
  "MetaFlag",
  "StageResult<T>",
]

[[layer]]
index = 2
name = "Constraint"
color = "#7c3aed"
base_z = 272.0
types = [
  "ConstraintEvaluation",
  "VendorConstraintSet",
  "InvoiceConstraintSolver",
  "InvoiceVerification",
  "Issue",
]

[[layer]]
index = 3
name = "Legal"
color = "#b91c1c"
base_z = 408.0
types = [
  "Z3Result",
  "LegalRule",
  "LegalSolver",
  "Jurisdiction",
  "TransactionFacts",
]

[[layer]]
index = 4
name = "FormalProof"
color = "#0f766e"
base_z = 544.0
types = ["KasuariSolver"]

[[layer]]
index = 5
name = "Attestation"
color = "#b45309"
base_z = 680.0
types = []  # PRD-6-FUTURE: InvariantEntry, AttestationSpec, InvariantRegistry
```

---

## Projection invariant

```toml
[projection_test]
input = { x = 192.0, y = 0.0, z = 0.0 }
scale = 1.0
origin = { x = 0.0, y = 0.0 }
expected = { screen_x = 166.272, screen_y = 96.0 }
tolerance = 0.01
```

Verification:
{{ cmd: cargo test -p ledger-core iso_project_matches_js_contract 2>&1 | grep -E "^test |FAILED" }}

